{
  "stem": "7069.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When he went into Poland, he would create these camps that, that eventually became extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Lithuania and wherever he went, he built concentration camps for a couple of reasons, I guess.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One of them, it was far away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The others were far away from the German population.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Although by that time, there are literally dozens of camps on German soil.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then-- and then also, of course, the eastern part of Europe had a great population of Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I suppose the transportation would be a little bit simpler to get 'em from the outlying areas right in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But this here was now Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this camp is still considered in the current annals of concentration camps as one, quote unquote, 'of the milder concentration camps.' I'd like to give you a couple of examples of a 'mild' concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "First of all, to talk about children-- it is known-- documented, in fact-- that during its existence of less than-- this camp's existence of less than three years, among all the people that were sent to this camp were approximately 15,000 children.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It is also known that less than 100 children in these less than three years survived, less than 100 children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were various reasons to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One of them, of course, was the transportations away from that camp to other camps, mostly Auschwitz, which there were also children involved.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But most of them died because of the circumstances of that camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One of the main reasons is the, the daily, quote unquote, 'menu.' Maybe it's a good idea if I, if I, if I describe that menu to you-- which, by the way, turned out the same in most of the-- in all the other camps.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was in a total of five different camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
